# Mirror the repo-root .kota/ ignore so a workflow's tmpdir-git inside this
# fixture sees realistic gitignore behavior (run artifacts under .kota/runs/
# stay untracked, matching production). Excluding .kota/ as a whole would
# block the outer repo from staging the fixture seed at
# .kota/runs/fxt-failed-builder-seed/, because git refuses to re-include
# files inside an excluded parent directory. Excluding only the contents
# (.kota/*) leaves the directory itself includable, then we selectively
# re-include the seed subtree.
.kota/*
!.kota/runs/
.kota/runs/*
!.kota/runs/fxt-failed-builder-seed/
node_modules/
